rows.label: qev050402_MSG0001
rows.name:
He is late. What is he thinking? Surely he would not
have turned craven and run at the last hour...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050402_MSG0002
rows.name: Hmm? Yes, human? Do you have business with me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050402_SEL0011
rows.name:
Announce that you have come to
fight De Sazon as De Ezich's proxy.

rows.label: qev050402_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask De Sazon what he is doing here.

rows.label: qev050402_MSG0003
rows.name: WHAT?! He will not come and fight himself?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050402_MSG0004
rows.name:
It is a private matter. Suffice it to say I must knock
some sense into a Wrothian...compatriot.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050402_MSG0005
rows.name:
I challenged him to battle and await him presently.
This place shall soon see combat, human.
I advise you to hurry on.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050402_MSG0006
rows.name: ...WHAT?! He sent you as a proxy to fight for him?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050402_MSG0007
rows.name:
Rrraaagh! Not only does he flout the Wrothian ways,
he casts aside his pride as well![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050402_MSG0008
rows.name:
I have had enough! I will defeat you here and now,
then go put an end to his cowardice for good![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050402_MSG0009
rows.name:
It is my responsibility as the one who brought him into
this world. And while you are an innocent pawn in my
son's games, I will not hesitate to cut you down![ST:wait ]
